[30;1m1705 | [0m[35mdef get_oneof_instance(cls, model_kwargs, constant_kwargs, model_arg=None):[0m
[30;1m1706 | [0m[35m    """[0m
[30;1m1707 | [0m[35m    Find the oneOf schema that matches the input data (e.g. payload).[0m
[30;1m1708 | [0m[35m    If exactly one schema matches the input data, an instance of that schema[0m
